name: shane fernett
text: Best pizza I've bought in 5 states, order fresh and youll never be disappointed. I always get a jumbo pizza with extra toppings and it comes out perfect every time. Auburn location is the best around!!!! 5 stars

name: Tony VanMeter
text: On time normally everything's what you ordered good pizza

name: Brian Dukes
text: It's ok for a small town joint. They usually run good specials. Not as good as other chains like pizza hut

name: Jaime Miller
text: Great tasting pizza. Friendly staff. My new favorite pizza!!!!
